<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="nl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Hybrid Cloud Demo</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 800px; margin: 50px auto; padding: 20px; }
        .azure { background: #0078d4; color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; }
        .esxi  { background: #607D8B; color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 20px; }
        h1 { margin-top: 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Hybrid Cloud Deployment</h1>

    <div class="azure">
        <h1>Azure VM (webserver)</h1>
        <p>Hostname: {{ ansible_hostname }}</p>
        <p>IP: {{ ansible_default_ipv4.address }}</p>
        <p>Deployed via: Terraform + Ansible + Docker Compose</p>
    </div>

    <div class="esxi">
        <h1>ESXi VM (database)</h1>
        <p>Host: hybrid-db-01 (lokaal netwerk)</p>
        <p>Service: MariaDB</p>
        <p>Deployed via: Terraform + Ansible (Galaxy role)</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
